column1: You're now almost finished the task! In the last part, you will do a final memory test. You will be shown an image, like below, on each trial, and you will be asked to indicate whether you have seen this image before (it is old) or you haven't not seen the image before (it is new)
Since the book is old, you should select 'old' because you have seen this image before.
This test is timed. You have a limit of 2 seconds to respond. So try to respond as quickly as possible.
First we will do a practice. When you’re ready to start the practice, press the space bar.
